{"name":"Sebastian Scarsdale","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Vel Calem, Vanguards","alignment":"Chaotic Neutral","hitDice":"10","armorName":"mage armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"85 (10d8 + 40)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"18","intPoints":"20","wisPoints":"18","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Legion of Undead","desc":"[MON]'s undead summons don't require concentration."},{"name":"Gloomlock Grimoire","desc":"[MON] has infinite 1st, 2nd, and 3rd level spell slots. 4th and 5th level spell slots cost 1-2 souls. When a creature dies, [MON] gains a soul. [MON] starts with 3 souls."},{"name":"Soulbind","desc":"When [MON] deals necrotic damage, it may curse a creature as the Void's magic knaws on their very soul. Cursed creatures lose their reactions and take [1d8] necrotic damage when it expends any resource."},{"name":"The Final Countdown","desc":"When [MON] dies, the Void Magic inside the Gloomlock Grimoire begins to unravel. In [1d4] turns, all creatures within 60ft. are cursed and take [3d10] necrotic damage (halved if they succeed a **DC [INT SAVE]** Con Save)."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON] is a spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC [INT SAVE], [INT ATK] to hit). [MON] has the following spells prepared:\n\n> Cantrips: _Toll the Dead, Chill Touch, Friends, Mind Sliver_\n> 1st level: _Dissonant Whispers, Bane, Ray of Sickness, Command, Inflict Wounds, Disguise Self_\n> 2nd level: _Wither & Bloom, Phantasmal Force, Darkness, Misty Step_\n> 3rd level: _Animate Dead, Summon Undead, Spirit Shroud, Fear, Speak with Dead, Counterspell_\n> 4th level: _Blight, Psychic Lance, Ego Whip_\n> 5th level: _Synaptic Static, Danse Macabre, Negative Energy Flood, Dominate Person_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Deadlock","desc":"Creatures cursed by [MON] take [INT 1d4] necrotic damage and lose their bonus actions until the end of their next turn."},{"name":"Supernova","desc":"[MON] unleashes a blast that damages all creatures around him. All creatures within 5ft. of [MON] take [3d10] force damage, halved if they succeed a **DC [INT SAVE]** Dex Save. [MON] then casts magic missile at 3rd level."},{"name":"Power Word: Kill","desc":"[MON] channels the power of the Void. If a creature is down, it instantly dies. [MON] gains 2 extra souls."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Sebastian","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}